The chief executive officer of
 Romania ’s  Banca Transilvania SA, (TLV)  Robert Rekkers, resigned, the
bank said in an e-mailed statement today.  Banca Transilvania appointed Peter Franklin as interim
delegated manager, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
